---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Smart Solutions - Refund Policy | Cutona"
  currentPage="refund-policy"
>
  <main>
    <!-- =========================
Refund guidelines section
===========================-->
    <section
      class="pt-32 pb-[100px] sm:pt-36 md:pt-42 md:pb-[200px] xl:pt-[180px]"
    >
      <div class="main-container">
        <div class="refund-policy space-y-[70px]">
          <div data-ns-animate data-delay="0.3" class="space-y-3">
            <h2>Return and refund guidelines</h2>
            <p>
              At Cutona, we are committed to providing you with the best
              possible service and experience. However, if for any reason our
              platform does not meet your expectations, we offer a simple and
              hassle-free refund policy.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div data-ns-animate data-delay="0.4" class="space-y-3">
            <h2>14-Day money-back guarantee</h2>
            <p>
              We are confident that you will love using Cutona. <br />
              Still, if you are not fully satisfied, we offer a full refund within
              14 days of your original purchase — no questions asked.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div data-ns-animate data-delay="0.5" class="space-y-3">
            <h2>Conditions for refund</h2>
            <p>You are eligible for a full refund if</p>
            <ul
              class="text-tagline-1 text-secondary/60 dark:text-accent/60 mt-6 list-inside space-y-3 font-normal"
            >
              <li>
                You request a refund within 14 days from the date of purchase.
              </li>
              <li>
                You can provide a valid reason if requested (optional but helps
                us improve).
              </li>
              <li>You request a refund after the 14-day period.</li>
              <li>You have violated our Terms and Conditions.</li>
              <li>
                You simply decide not to use the product anymore without a valid
                issue.
              </li>
              <li>
                You requested a refund for issues already resolved by our
                support team.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div data-ns-animate data-delay="0.4" class="space-y-3">
            <h2>How to request a refund</h2>
            <p>Simply follow these easy steps</p>
            <ol class="mt-8 mb-6 space-y-8">
              <li data-ns-animate data-delay="0.5">
                <div
                  class="bg-background-1 dark:bg-background-6 flex max-w-[596px] items-start gap-4 rounded-2xl px-7 py-5 sm:gap-[22px] sm:rounded-[20px] sm:px-[34px] sm:py-6"
                >
                  <div
                    class="bg-ns-yellow text-tagline-1 text-secondary flex size-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full font-semibold"
                  >
                    1
                  </div>
                  <div class="space-y-1">
                    <p
                      class="text-tagline-1 text-secondary dark:text-accent leading-[27px] font-medium sm:text-lg"
                    >
                      Submit a support ticket through our [Contact Page].
                    </p>
                    <p>
                      If you're experiencing any issues or need assistance, our
                      support team is here to help. Simply visit our [Contact
                      Page] and fill out the support ticket form with the
                      relevant details.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li data-ns-animate data-delay="0.6">
                <div
                  class="bg-background-1 dark:bg-background-6 flex max-w-[596px] items-start gap-4 rounded-2xl px-7 py-5 sm:gap-[22px] sm:rounded-[20px] sm:px-[34px] sm:py-6"
                >
                  <div
                    class="bg-ns-green text-tagline-1 text-secondary flex size-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full font-semibold"
                  >
                    2
                  </div>
                  <div class="space-y-1">
                    <p
                      class="text-tagline-1 text-secondary dark:text-accent leading-[27px] font-medium sm:text-lg"
                    >
                      Share your order ID, email, and a quick description.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                      Once we receive this information, our team will review it
                      and get back to you as soon as possible. Thank you for
                      your cooperation!
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li data-ns-animate data-delay="0.7">
                <div
                  class="bg-background-1 dark:bg-background-6 flex max-w-[596px] items-start gap-4 rounded-2xl px-7 py-5 sm:gap-[22px] sm:rounded-[20px] sm:px-[34px] sm:py-6"
                >
                  <div
                    class="bg-ns-cyan text-tagline-1 text-secondary flex size-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full font-semibold"
                  >
                    3
                  </div>
                  <div class="space-y-1">
                    <p
                      class="text-tagline-1 text-secondary dark:text-accent leading-[27px] font-medium sm:text-lg"
                    >
                      Our team will review and process your refund request.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                      Thank you for reaching out. We’ve received your refund
                      request and our team is currently reviewing the details.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ol>
            <p data-ns-animate data-delay="0.7">
              Refunds will be issued to the
              <span class="text-secondary dark:text-accent"
                >original payment method</span
              >
              used at checkout.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div data-ns-animate data-delay="0.8" class="space-y-3">
            <h2>Refund processing time</h2>
            <p>
              Once your refund is approved, it may take 5–10 business days for
              the amount to reflect in your bank statement, depending on your
              payment provider.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div data-ns-animate data-delay="0.9" class="space-y-3">
            <h2>Non-refundable situations</h2>
            <p>
              Cutona reserves the right to suspend or terminate any user account
              without prior notice for reasons including but not limited to
            </p>
            <ul
              class="text-tagline-1 text-secondary/60 dark:text-accent/60 mt-6 list-inside space-y-3 font-normal"
            >
              <li>Purchases made through unauthorized sources.</li>
              <li>
                Requests based on lack of features not available in the product
                description.
              </li>
              <li>Downgrades from a higher-tier plan after extensive usage.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div data-ns-animate data-delay="0.8" class="space-y-3">
            <h2>We appreciate your feedback</h2>
            <p>
              If you choose to request a refund, we would be grateful if you
              could let us know why. Your feedback helps us improve Cutona for
              future users!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- =========================
CTA v1 section
===========================-->
    <section class="py-[50px] md:py-20 lg:py-28" aria-label="Use Case Overview">
      <div class="main-container">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-between lg:flex-row">
          <div
            class="w-full space-y-5 text-center max-[400px]:max-w-[300px] lg:max-w-[476px] lg:text-left xl:max-w-[650px]"
          >
            <span
              data-ns-animate
              data-delay="0.3"
              class="badge badge-green badge-yellow-v2">Get started</span
            >
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h2
                data-ns-animate
                data-delay="0.4"
                class="text-secondary dark:text-accent text-heading-5 sm:text-heading-4 lg:text-heading-3 xl:text-heading-2"
              >
                Ready to start earning with Cutona?
                <span class="text-primary-500 hidden">Get started today</span>
              </h2>
              <p data-ns-animate data-delay="0.5">
                If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to our team.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div
            class="w-full space-y-6 pt-[40px] sm:w-[80%] md:ml-0 md:w-[70%] lg:basis-[530px] lg:pt-[67px] xl:ml-[60px]"
          >
            <form
              data-ns-animate
              data-delay="0.6"
              action="#"
              method="post"
              class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-5 sm:flex-row lg:gap-3"
            >
              <input
                type="email"
                name="email"
                id="userEmail-cta-v1"
                placeholder="Enter your email"
                required
                class="shadow-1 placeholder:text-secondary/50 border-stroke-1 dark:border-stroke-7 dark:placeholder:text-accent/60 focus:border-primary-600 dark:focus:border-primary-400 dark:text-accent h-12 w-full rounded-2xl border px-[18px] py-3 font-normal placeholder:font-normal focus:outline-none max-[376px]:w-full md:w-[61%] lg:max-w-[340px] xl:h-13 xl:w-[71%]"
              />

              <button
                type="submit"
                class="bg-primary-500 text-tagline-1 w-full cursor-pointer rounded-2xl px-1 py-1 font-normal text-white sm:w-auto"
                data-button-v3
              >
                <div class="flex items-center gap-x-4">
                  <!-- icon   -->
                  <span
                    class="fill-secondary relative z-20 flex size-10 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-[13px] bg-white transition-all duration-700 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1)] xl:size-11"
                    data-button-v3-icon
                    aria-hidden="true"
                  >
                    <svg
                      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                      class="size-6"
                    >
                      <path d="M11 5H13V7H11V5Z"></path>
                      <path d="M5 5H7V7H5V5Z"></path>
                      <path d="M14 8H16V10H14V8Z"></path>
                      <path d="M8 8H10V10H8V8Z"></path>
                      <path d="M17 11H19V13H17V11Z"></path>
                      <path d="M11 11H13V13H11V11Z"></path>
                      <path d="M14 14H16V16H14V14Z"></path>
                      <path d="M8 14H10V16H8V14Z"></path>
                      <path d="M11 17H13V19H11V17Z"></path>
                      <path d="M5 17H7V19H5V17Z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <!-- content  -->
                  <span
                    class="shrink-0 stroke-0 pr-4 transition-all duration-700 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1)] first-letter:uppercase"
                    data-button-v3-text
                    aria-hidden="true"
                  >
                    Get started
                  </span>
                </div>
              </button>
            </form>
            <ul
              class="flex flex-row items-center justify-center gap-x-4 gap-y-5 sm:gap-x-6 sm:gap-y-0 lg:justify-start"
            >
              <li
                data-ns-animate
                data-delay="0.7"
                class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
              >
                <span
                  class="bg-secondary dark:bg-accent flex size-[18px] items-center justify-center rounded-full"
                >
                  <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="10"
                    height="7"
                    viewBox="0 0 10 7"
                    fill="none"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                    class="dark:fill-secondary fill-white"
                  >
                    <path
                      d="M4.31661 6.75605L9.74905 1.42144C10.0836 1.0959 10.0836 0.569702 9.74905 0.244158C9.41446 -0.081386 8.87363 -0.081386 8.53904 0.244158L3.7116 4.99012L1.46096 2.78807C1.12636 2.46253 0.585538 2.46253 0.250945 2.78807C-0.0836483 3.11362 -0.0836483 3.63982 0.250945 3.96536L3.1066 6.75605C3.27347 6.91841 3.49253 7 3.7116 7C3.93067 7 4.14974 6.91841 4.31661 6.75605Z"
                    ></path>
                  </svg>
                </span>
                <p class="text-tagline-3 sm:text-tagline-2">
                  No credit card required
                </p>
              </li>
              <li
                data-ns-animate
                data-delay="0.8"
                class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
              >
                <span
                  class="bg-secondary dark:bg-accent flex size-[18px] items-center justify-center rounded-full"
                >
                  <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="10"
                    height="7"
                    viewBox="0 0 10 7"
                    fill="none"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                    class="dark:fill-secondary fill-white"
                  >
                    <path
                      d="M4.31661 6.75605L9.74905 1.42144C10.0836 1.0959 10.0836 0.569702 9.74905 0.244158C9.41446 -0.081386 8.87363 -0.081386 8.53904 0.244158L3.7116 4.99012L1.46096 2.78807C1.12636 2.46253 0.585538 2.46253 0.250945 2.78807C-0.0836483 3.11362 -0.0836483 3.63982 0.250945 3.96536L3.1066 6.75605C3.27347 6.91841 3.49253 7 3.7116 7C3.93067 7 4.14974 6.91841 4.31661 6.75605Z"
                    ></path>
                  </svg>
                </span>
                <p class="text-tagline-3 sm:text-tagline-2">
                  14-Day free trial
                </p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
